<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-96A5D381-A194-46C6-A9C8-44213DC90AC7" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-96A5D381-A194-46C6-A9C8-44213DC90AC7" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">01 How to adjust the tension of the curing carriage drive belt</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-173AF84C-D126-4DD5-8ABA-ADD08113B9D4"><p class="- topic/p ">This adjustment is the mechanical belt tension of the curing carriage belt. The adjustment needs to be done only at the installation of new drive belt. 
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-1DB9579F-E05E-497C-B59D-BFC9A1268399"><p class="- topic/p ">This adjustment can only be done after the mechanical release of the belt tension of the carriage belt. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">The adjustment must be done before the start-up (initialization) of the printer. 
</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">After the initialization of the printer the position of the bolt has no reference anymore. 
</p></note></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Adjustment</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_A392D23B9FA5434A8095E72A33F001E1" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_BFC835835B5440A98A2DF72417BDB02D" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Screwdriver 
</p></li><li id="LI_290738A2E21242D1A21ED2B5C14AE640" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_224C2BD92AB546E2898078FF4634DE8F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-25AA7B7A-247E-4273-9BBE-0C944C037E02-low.png" id="IMAGE_135153AEFA7545298AA11B6DB0437413" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-25AA7B7A-247E-4273-9BBE-0C944C037E02-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to adjust</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Turn the bolt (-A-) completely in. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-811C1A95-B961-44FD-821C-52FEB940233C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CFAA38F3-11E2-4D3D-923A-2344975BC02F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CFAA38F3-11E2-4D3D-923A-2344975BC02F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Move the tension bracket (-B-) to the right hand side. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-3CA7BC78-DDC7-4587-B709-B0E02FD8138D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-206146F8-E191-4137-B804-9E433D8243D3-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-206146F8-E191-4137-B804-9E433D8243D3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Press on the tension plate (-C-). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the tension bracket with a screwdriver (-D-). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-5955F7B9-0BEE-485F-9F6F-0CF96F17E1AF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FB8E826F-16F7-4884-82CF-ECA8E93834D7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FB8E826F-16F7-4884-82CF-ECA8E93834D7-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_CC316D3E80544FC5BDDC9EA94B11707F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6678B8E2-DA0C-4A1E-A48B-92A8DCF66F3C-low.png" id="IMAGE_8EDEFF67765F49B59C211565E1063D60" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6678B8E2-DA0C-4A1E-A48B-92A8DCF66F3C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the pulley (-E-) and mount the drive belt (-F-). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_B1B1764FA9B9462DAE7AC5C0641B3774" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-BAD58BE4-BB7A-4D32-AFD5-8BA092239E8A-low.png" id="IMAGE_A9DF71196DB946679D70C2D9F1658294" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BAD58BE4-BB7A-4D32-AFD5-8BA092239E8A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Hook the drive belt (2x) in the curing carriage assembly. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-4FDB8B2D-C24C-4FB1-8864-FFDFFBDB3932" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0822DB00-062C-4506-95AC-4633957256EB-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0822DB00-062C-4506-95AC-4633957256EB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screwdriver (used to lock the position of the bracket). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_A29437F7CD18417B866B0878501AAB16" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6678B8E2-DA0C-4A1E-A48B-92A8DCF66F3C-low.png" id="IMAGE_B161228AAA1541F3BCF9C4710667A47F" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6678B8E2-DA0C-4A1E-A48B-92A8DCF66F3C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Turn the bolt (-A-) counter clock-wise till the edge of the bolt is set to 0 +/- 0.5 mm. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_AEEB5781278B45C0AADAABC2ECF1BE07" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B8BB8116-9752-4592-97F1-2911F7707081-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B8BB8116-9752-4592-97F1-2911F7707081-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-1F897B6A-3B52-4EA1-AC18-9626A9B429D4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Adjustment</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
